## Phase 4 — Advanced Features (Week 9-11)

> **Goal:** Forking, CLI upgrade, more languages

### 4.1 Repository Forking

#### [MODIFY] [repositories.js](file:///d:/code-classroom/backend/src/routes/repositories.js)
- `POST /api/repositories/fork` — clone repo files into new repo
- Track `forked_from` field
- Show fork count on repo cards

### 4.2 CLI Upgrade

#### [MODIFY] `cli/`
- `collab login` — interactive login, store JWT in `~/.collab/config.json`
- `collab clone <repo-url>` — init + pull in one command
- `collab branch` / `collab checkout` / `collab merge`
- `collab status` (alias for `collab check`)

### 4.3 Additional Languages

#### [MODIFY] [terminal.js](file:///d:/code-classroom/backend/src/routes/terminal.js) + [run.js](file:///d:/code-classroom/backend/src/routes/run.js)
- Add C/C++ support: `gcc:latest` Docker image
- Add JavaScript/Node.js: `node:20-alpine`
- Language auto-detection from file extension

### 4.4 UI Enhancements

- Stars count on repos (like/favorite system)
- Repository size display
- Language breakdown bar (like GitHub)
- Contributor avatars

